dct_title_s: Administrative map of Yosemite National Park, California
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours and spot heights.; At head of title: Department of the Interior.; "Surveyed in 1893-94, 1896, 1898-99, and 1905."; Contour interval 100 feet. Datum is mean sea level.; U.S. township and section lines and section corners are shown.; Shows park limits established by various Acts of Congress.
